<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c3">{وَانْظُرْ إِلَى إِلَهِكَ الَّذِي ظَلْتَ}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ٩٧]</span> صِرْتَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{عَلَيْهِ عَاكِفًا}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ٩٧]</span> عَابِدًا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ السُّدِّيُّ:</span> <span class="c3">{ظَلْتَ عَلَيْهِ عَاكِفًا}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ٩٧]</span> يَعْنِي أَقَمْتَ عَلَيْهِ عَابِدًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> <span class="c3">{لَنُحَرِّقَنَّهُ}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ٩٧]</span> قَالَ يَحْيَى: سَمِعْتُ بَعْضَ الْكُوفِيِّينَ يَقُولُ: لَنُبَرِّدَنَّهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{ثُمَّ لَنَنْسِفَنَّهُ فِي الْيَمِّ نَسْفًا}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ٩٧]</span> وَقَالَ الْكَلْبِيُّ: ذَبَحَهُ مُوسَى، ثُمَّ أَحْرَقَهُ بِالنَّارِ، ثُمَّ ذَرَاهُ فِي الْبَحْرِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَهُوَ فِي قَوْلِ مَنْ قَالَ هَذَا أَنَّهُ تَحَوَّلَ لَحْمًا وَدَمًا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c3">{لَنَنْسِفَنَّهُ}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ٩٧]</span> هُوَ حِينَ ذَرَاهُ فِي الْبَحْرِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c3">{إِنَّمَا إِلَهُكُمُ اللَّهُ الَّذِي لا إِلَهَ إِلا هُوَ وَسِعَ كُلَّ شَيْءٍ عِلْمًا}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ٩٨]</span> سَعِيدٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ قَتَادَةَ قَالَ:</span> مَلأَ كُلَّ شَيْءٍ عِلْمًا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ يَحْيَى:</span> أَيْ لا يَكُونُ شَيْءٌ إِلا بِعِلْمِ اللَّهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c3">{كَذَلِكَ نَقُصُّ عَلَيْكَ مِنْ أَنْبَاءِ مَا قَدْ سَبَقَ}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ٩٩]</span> مِنْ أَخْبَارِ مَا قَدْ مَضَى.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c3">{وَقَدْ آتَيْنَاكَ}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ٩٩]</span> أَيْ: وَقَدْ أَعْطَيْنَاكَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c3">{مِنْ لَدُنَّا}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ٩٩]</span> مِنْ عِنْدِنَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c3">{ذِكْرًا}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ٩٩]</span> الْقُرْآنَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c3">{مَنْ أَعْرَضَ عَنْهُ}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ١٠٠]</span> عَنِ الْقُرْآنِ وَلَمْ يُؤْمِنْ بِهِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c3">{فَإِنَّهُ يَحْمِلُ يَوْمَ الْقِيَامَةِ وِزْرًا}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ١٠٠]</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>